An artist at heart, Belarus-born Oksana has built a career as a freelance illustrator. 🎨⁠
⁠
Her library of work includes children's books, collaborations with young worldwide brands, and she also owns a small shop for her illustrations and prints.⁠
⁠

Good energy is contagious. So we wanted to share some #mindfulmonday tips for you to reach your inner "whoosah!" 🧘‍♀️✨⁠
⁠
This weeks tip, 5-Min Mindfulness: ⁠
1. Find a calm space & close your eyes⁠
2. Inhale through your nose & out your mouth slowly.⁠
3. Repeat process for 3-5 mins.⁠
⁠
Ta da! You've done your 1st session! People who meditate are less stressed, healthier, sleep better, & is more positive towards life. ✌️⁠
